story.text: Drove to Missoula last night. Another good drive. Talked to many friends a family. Had a great breakfast with Kerr this morning. Really enjoyable.
Now meeting with the Western Director of the Land Trust Alliance. Very excited to see where this relationship might lead.
Meeting with Ward soon, also really excited to see where his tug boat takes us.
